  "detailed_description": "<h1>Follow Us</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1635834634\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>History</strong></h2>Discover the story behind a boy who has a touching reality.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/4a4049d3baba3d15088e66d0400fb343.poster.avif?t=1635834634\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/4a4049d3baba3d15088e66d0400fb343.webm?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/4a4049d3baba3d15088e66d0400fb343.mp4?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experiences</strong></h2>The scenes will be based on this boy's narrative through puzzle pieces, which will tell the moments of sadness and happiness experienced by him.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/2602d6dbf9d09fcfd18a85675d5bcd22.poster.avif?t=1635834634\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/2602d6dbf9d09fcfd18a85675d5bcd22.webm?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/2602d6dbf9d09fcfd18a85675d5bcd22.mp4?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenges</strong></h2>Each art will have its respective difficulty, making the game interactive and challenging.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/46aa762a83ad6ca70cb6b929628cc797.poster.avif?t=1635834634\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/46aa762a83ad6ca70cb6b929628cc797.webm?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/46aa762a83ad6ca70cb6b929628cc797.mp4?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pleasant</strong></h2>With soft music and a relaxing atmosphere, enjoy this experience by assembling and remounting the game's many challenges.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/7d62e15117bd73956194f45f309a2410.poster.avif?t=1635834634\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/7d62e15117bd73956194f45f309a2410.webm?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792230/extras/7d62e15117bd73956194f45f309a2410.mp4?t=1635834634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
